            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 mb-md-0">
                    <h5 class="text-dark mb-3">Cool Company</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted">Providing innovative solutions for businesses since 2025. Our mission is to
                        help our clients succeed through cutting-edge technology.</p>
